1075
00:58:07,898 --> 00:58:08,148
Rym: "Date?

1076
00:58:08,990 --> 00:58:09,075
Rym: Girl?

1077
00:58:09,993 --> 00:58:11,790
Rym: Yeah, you know, as in female.

1078
00:58:12,335 --> 00:58:12,570
Rym: Pretty?

1079
00:58:13,250 --> 00:58:13,590
Rym: Carol.

1080
00:58:14,830 --> 00:58:14,913
Rym: Mine.".

1081
00:58:15,571 --> 00:58:19,510
Rym: Each of the last four words was accompanied by a hard poke from the forefinger.

1082
00:58:20,079 --> 00:58:20,428
Rym: Uh-oh.

1083
00:58:21,031 --> 00:58:21,630
Rym: Tim had forgotten.

1084
00:58:22,490 --> 00:58:24,130
Rym: Carol had a boyfriend.

1085
00:58:24,872 --> 00:58:26,049
Rym: A big boyfriend.

1086
00:58:26,890 --> 00:58:28,910
Rym: Maybe she was getting ready to dump him, though.

1087
00:58:29,431 --> 00:58:29,869
Rym: No matter.

1088
00:58:30,270 --> 00:58:34,610
Rym: Tim was still dead meat if Donkey Kong here thought he was trespassing on his territory.

1089
00:58:35,336 --> 00:58:35,585
Rym: "Oh, that?

1090
00:58:35,992 --> 00:58:36,829
Rym: Uh, gee, Burt.

1091
00:58:37,271 --> 00:58:39,027
Rym: She just wants me to take her shopping for video

1092
00:58:39,048 --> 00:58:39,270
