00:58:40,091 --> 00:58:43,549
Rym: "The video jockey wants to ride off into the sunset with my girl, huh?

1094
00:58:43,873 --> 00:58:44,909
Rym: Well, pal, let me tell you.

1095
00:58:45,411 --> 00:58:49,189
Rym: I'm perfectly capable of taking Carol to any store she wants to go to.

1096
00:58:49,651 --> 00:58:54,084
Rym: But I tell you, I feel like putting you out of commission just for thinking about going out with my

1097
00:58:54,146 --> 00:58:54,330
