1117
00:59:25,231 --> 00:59:25,769
Rym: "Move it, man.

1118
00:59:25,971 --> 00:59:27,107
Rym: I'll be waiting for you right

1119
00:59:27,148 --> 00:59:27,290
Rym: here.".

1120
00:59:28,210 --> 00:59:29,910
Rym: Tim pushed through the swinging door.

1121
00:59:30,390 --> 00:59:33,670
Rym: He went to a sink, ran cold water, and splashed it on his face.

1122
00:59:34,370 --> 00:59:37,010
Rym: Boy oh boy oh boy was he in trouble.

1123
00:59:37,731 --> 00:59:38,304
Rym: What was he gonna do?

1124
00:59:39,190 --> 00:59:41,642
Rym: The word around the school was the last kid who crossed.

