00:59:42,044 --> 00:59:45,470
Rym: Alvin was wearing concrete braces at the bottom of Bulmer Pond.

1127
00:59:46,391 --> 00:59:55,190
Rym: Tim was pretty good when it came to wrestling Hulk Hogan or Macho Man on his Nintendo trademark, but when it came to real life, he wasn't the kind of kid to fight much.

